Hi,

this is the call for the next video conference of the Debian Med team
that are an established means to organise the tasks inside our team.
As an exception we do not meet at 17th as usual but on 21th since this
is one day before the Debian Science BoF will happen at DebConf

of a month.  Usually it takes us only 15-20min depending what we are
talking about and how many people are joining.  The next meeting is
tomorrow 18:00 UTC

     https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=Debian+CoViD-19+Biohackathon+Video+Conference&iso=20220721T18

The meeting is on the Debian Social channel

     https://jitsi.debian.social/DebianMedCovid19

The main topic is to provide input for the Debian Science BoF

Lets keep on the great work and see you on Thursday

       Andreas.

